issue.body:
Update Gradle Wrapper and build to 7.0.
Update Spotless to 5.12.1.
Update Linux Packaging plugin to 8.5.6.
Update Download Task plugin to 4.1.1.
Update install4j plugin:

 - Disable installers task if Java < 11, no longed functional;
 - Set up toolchain to build ZAP with Java 8 when releasing and update
 release workflows to use Java 11.

Update Launch4j plugin to 2.5.0.
Update JaCoCo to 0.5.6.

Fix #6511.
